data.title: The Anderson Clinic
data.meta_description: The Anderson Clinic provides traditional and unique therapies for those overcoming mental health issues. Offering Ketamine Infusion therapy and PrTMS
data.text:
PSYCHOTHERAPY

Psychotherapy is a medical term for traditional talk therapy and counseling to help explore needs and overcome personal obstacles standing in the way of optimal mental health. We provide counseling therapy in a safe, confidential, and judgement-free space, and remind everyone that therapy—like visiting a doctor for a high fever—is a normal part of wellness and nothing to be ashamed or nervous about. Learn More

Ketamine Infusions

Ketamine is an anesthetic and analgesic used in medicine since the Vietnam War. Medical researchers and clinicians recently discovered that very low IV doses of ketamine offers rapid relief from severe depression even when other medications have failed. Learn More

Medication management

We work with individual patients under our care, patients under the care of other doctors, as well as psychiatry residents and clinicians to ensure a safe and effective medication program. Learn More
